🗣Representatives of three IT companies from the Netherlands will help modernize Ukrainian UAVs, the Minister of Defense of the country told about this in an exclusive interview with a Radio Liberty journalist.

According to Kaisa Ollongren, the Ukrainian defense industry has many prospects for development, and the production and modernization of drones is one of the promising areas. The minister arrived in Kyiv together with representatives of three companies for cooperation with Ukraine

